data.description: Wonderful home on over 1/2 acre near shopping, schools and restaurants with easy access to IH-10 and only minutes from Beaumont or15-20 minutes to the Louisiana line! Large living room with vaulted ceilings and wood burning fireplace, spacious kitchen with black stainless appliances connected to breakfast area and don't miss the huge storage room/pantry off the laundry room! Sunroom leads to the great big backyard that is fully fenced with double gate access to the driveway. Lots of playing room here! This home is sure to please, make your appt TODAY!
